{"tid":193842,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★面對？不了！Surface已超越ipad取得第一名！","createTime":"2017-04-09T14:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T10:57:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93862bb0cafd2b661f3dd3f2cf1f94b82c354f70","tid":193842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/08/surface-beats-ipad-j-d-power/notebook/tablet-notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2Fsurface-beats-ipad-j-d-power%2Fnotebook%2Ftablet-notebook%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c9200eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/08/surface-beats-ipad-j-d-power/notebook/tablet-notebook/</a><br />\n<br />\n在平板電腦市場，iPad 一向都獲得較高的市佔率，不過近年競爭對手也沒有在一味捱打，Microsoft 的 Surface 就取得不錯的成績，在滿意度調查中更超越 iPad 取得首位。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國 J.D. Power 的 2017 年美國平板電腦滿意度調查，Microsoft 的 Surface 系列在 1000 分總分之中取得 855 分，比 iPad 系列高出 6 分，首次取得第一位。這個調查從 2016 年 10 月到 12 月之間，訪問了 2,238 名擁有裝置不足一年的用家，讓他們就平板電腦的不同方面給予評價，包括效能（28%）、操作難度（22%）、功能（22%）、設計和外觀（17%）和售價（11%）。"},{"pid":"b15ee9a15290808902d405263f075284af526650","tid":193842,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"Apple已死"},{"pid":"748c45760d6ca95623c5e5f9be125d1fb3121f2d","tid":193842,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"ifandog不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f546cf009d98a44034bb43c041de30ac63d14ca","tid":193842,"uid":4677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"悶唔撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cc64fae366123a3a5acaca2596